Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.36,1:20:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.30,1:20:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,奈美
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.77,1:20:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.98,1:20:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,轉過來正面
