Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.67,1:39:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續插進去哦
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.54,1:39:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.82,1:39:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 自己動起來
