Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.34,1:52:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,有試過這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.49,1:52:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 讓我好好看看你的身體
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.45,1:53:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的姿勢 期待什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.02,1:53:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,發出很棒的叫聲啊
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.63,1:54:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.64,1:54:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊\N不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.18,1:54:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣濕漉漉的不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.05,1:54:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.14,1:54:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒的叫聲哦
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.71,1:55:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢的按摩這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.47,1:55:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.95,1:56:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴的汁液漸漸出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.28,1:56:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,很期待是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.90,1:56:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這個地方是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.99,1:56:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡也要
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.68,1:57:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.02,1:57:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續讓我好好看看身體
Dialogue: 0,1:57:21.03,1:57:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,張開腿
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.17,1:57:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.50,1:57:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,自己好好看看
Dialogue: 0,1:57:35.71,1:57:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:57:58.13,1:57:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.87,1:58:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的 好好感覺一下\N好舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:59:23.55,1:59:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,把手舉起來
Dialogue: 0,1:59:29.42,1:59:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來全部塗抹精油哦
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.98,2:02:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,腿張開一點
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.85,2:02:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續啊
Dialogue: 0,2:02:22.00,2:02:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續啊 張開一點
Dialogue: 0,2:02:34.94,2:02:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好興奮吧
Dialogue: 0,2:02:40.15,2:02:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服\N舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,2:02:52.56,2:02:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續是吧
Dialogue: 0,2:04:15.18,2:04:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,很不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,2:04:19.71,2:04:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,過來這裡
Dialogue: 0,2:04:37.87,2:04:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,結果 還是想要這個吧
Dialogue: 0,2:04:47.21,2:04:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡怎麼樣都可以
Dialogue: 0,2:05:53.94,2:05:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋蛋也要摸
Dialogue: 0,2:06:31.58,2:06:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,想要含住吧
Dialogue: 0,2:06:38.92,2:06:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,2:06:41.32,2:06:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,說一下 想要
Dialogue: 0,2:06:45.73,2:06:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,想要
Dialogue: 0,2:06:48.66,2:06:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,想要肉棒
Dialogue: 0,2:06:55.07,2:07:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,想要肉棒\N想要是吧
Dialogue: 0,2:07:01.74,2:07:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 接下來這裡
Dialogue: 0,2:07:08.55,2:07:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,過來這裡
Dialogue: 0,2:07:19.23,2:07:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,到上面來
Dialogue: 0,2:07:46.05,2:07:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,2:07:49.39,2:07:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,插進去裡面
Dialogue: 0,2:07:55.80,2:07:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,2:08:44.51,2:08:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴好熱哦
Dialogue: 0,2:08:49.98,2:08:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:08:52.39,2:08:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好緊
Dialogue: 0,2:10:30.08,2:10:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續看看淫蕩的小穴
Dialogue: 0,2:10:40.76,2:10:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續動起來
Dialogue: 0,2:10:44.50,2:10:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,2:11:06.52,2:11:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:11:09.46,2:11:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:11:32.15,2:11:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:11:38.29,2:11:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,2:11:41.09,2:11:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,插進去裡面 好舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,2:11:50.56,2:11:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,看看啊
Dialogue: 0,2:11:53.37,2:11:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒插進去的地方
Dialogue: 0,2:12:01.91,2:12:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看看
Dialogue: 0,2:12:12.05,2:12:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,2:12:26.87,2:12:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,2:12:32.07,2:12:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,2:12:36.61,2:12:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,2:12:47.69,2:12:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,2:13:08.91,2:13:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:13:18.79,2:13:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好敏感吧
Dialogue: 0,2:13:23.32,2:13:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,過來這裡
Dialogue: 0,2:13:30.26,2:13:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股給我
Dialogue: 0,2:13:46.41,2:13:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,進去裡面哦
Dialogue: 0,2:13:50.42,2:13:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,進去了
Dialogue: 0,2:15:08.50,2:15:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了 高潮了 高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:16:19.77,2:16:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了 高潮了 高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:16:48.33,2:16:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,抵住是吧 繼續
Dialogue: 0,2:17:28.64,2:17:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,2:17:48.66,2:17:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:18:00.53,2:18:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 動起來
Dialogue: 0,2:18:22.96,2:18:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服是吧
Dialogue: 0,2:18:42.18,2:18:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是吧
Dialogue: 0,2:18:45.51,2:18:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是吧
Dialogue: 0,2:18:48.85,2:18:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡
Dialogue: 0,2:18:53.25,2:18:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:19:02.86,2:19:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,2:19:07.53,2:19:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:19:21.28,2:19:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,2:19:46.91,2:19:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,2:20:37.76,2:20:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這個樣子沒有試過吧
Dialogue: 0,2:20:58.18,2:20:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,2:21:01.11,2:21:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了 高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:21:07.65,2:21:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,2:22:17.86,2:22:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,2:22:28.00,2:22:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,想要更多吧\N繼續插進去裡面
Dialogue: 0,2:22:34.27,2:22:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是吧
Dialogue: 0,2:22:38.68,2:22:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續插進去
Dialogue: 0,2:22:42.82,2:22:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,2:22:46.55,2:22:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,2:22:50.42,2:22:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,全部射到我的臉上
Dialogue: 0,2:23:04.84,2:23:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:23:28.46,2:23:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,2:23:38.34,2:23:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,2:23:42.21,2:23:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:24:07.17,2:24:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續含住
Dialogue: 0,2:24:43.34,2:24:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我說了 好癢啊\N沒事
Dialogue: 0,2:24:50.01,2:24:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 我再問一下\N真的和奈美結婚啊
Dialogue: 0,2:24:54.81,2:25:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要結婚啊 說什麼結婚之前\N做愛沒意義 一直守著
Dialogue: 0,2:25:02.29,2:25:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是很好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,2:25:04.69,2:25:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 一直守著啊
Dialogue: 0,2:25:07.89,2:25:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,果然 好喜歡按摩啊
Dialogue: 0,2:25:10.56,2:25:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,也許是吧
Dialogue: 0,2:25:13.90,2:25:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不是處女更加舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,2:25:18.30,2:25:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我們兩人真是壞
Dialogue: 0,2:25:24.04,2:25:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 和你更加興奮
Dialogue: 0,2:25:28.31,2:25:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,騙人吧
Dialogue: 0,2:25:30.32,2:25:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真是變態的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,2:25:32.85,2:25:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,2:25:36.46,2:25:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,小變態 再來一次吧
Dialogue: 0,2:25:38.99,2:25:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 來吧
Dialogue: 0,2:25:44.86,2:25:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 她也嘗試了那個按摩
Dialogue: 0,2:25:49.67,2:25:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,2:25:52.21,2:25:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,做了吧
Dialogue: 0,2:25:53.67,2:25:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼說這個
Dialogue: 0,2:25:56.48,2:25:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,行了
Dialogue: 0,2:26:06.09,2:26:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,（星野奈美）
Dialogue: 0,2:26:09.82,2:26:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,（導演 前田文豪）
Dialogue: 0,2:26:18.23,2:26:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝觀賞
